If it need to support VS2015 , we can't update the vcxproj directly. You can add new project setting files for VS2015. 

It's better to add some different project files and let the developer to choose what VS version they want.

Please do not open new pull-requests, when an existing pull-request exists for the same change/jira. It is better to just push new commits onto the same branch so that we can see previous commits & changes.

If it is absolutely necessary to do so, then it is good idea to put comment in the older one and close it.

Because the file format has been changed, resulting in a very large difference, so close this request, and create a new pullrequest to commit code. 
The latest pull-request is in the following link https://github.com/apache/incubator-trafodion/pull/1353
The old pull-request is already closed with related comment, thanks.
@venkat1m, could you point to the source code for the UDF event_log_reader so that @gpj1987 can change that as well?
@selvaganesang, are you happy with this change now? Is it time to merge it?
